{"tid":1030921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"創科局公佈 機讀/人讀格式開放數據計劃","createTime":"2019-02-21T10:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T01:51:03.000Z","uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"78560069e41c960ea98e1184db7126b8ae516b05","tid":1030921,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:00:33.000Z","msg":"創新及科技局 Innovation and Technology Bureau HK<br />\nLike This Page &middot; 19 hrs &middot; <br />\n <br />\n今日有報道指，用機讀格式公布開放數據計劃嘅清單會好啲。同樣嘅資料，A同B兩種形式，你會睇得明邊種？<br />\n<br />\n#機讀格式資料要用電腦程式解讀先易明<br />\n#有需要嘅話用晒兩種形式公布都得<br />\n#公布清單係想畀公眾同業界了解各局同部門開放數據集嘅計劃同時間表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1Fz0fF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1Fz0fF.jpg&h=da5d6def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ITBHK/photos/a.1689124714671352/2214961552087663/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FITBHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.1689124714671352%2F2214961552087663%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=37613675\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ITBHK/photos/a.1689124714671352/2214961552087663/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局 Innovation and Technology Bureau HK 謝謝您們的意見😊。這個post是想展示如果單純以機讀格式去公布開放數據計劃，反而有機會令一般公眾難以理解。但既然有意見認為值得以機讀格式公布清單，資科辦當然會從善如流😉，考慮公眾嘅建議，在網頁版外多加個機讀格式啦。早前有關報道指各政策局和部門的開放數據計劃清單只有網頁版本而沒有機讀格式版本，不方便市民。事實上，開放數據計劃下，所有在「資料一線通」網站開放的數據均會以CSV, JSON, XML等機讀格式發放。"},{"pid":"a9c892e3cbae25c9bb4713b46048c6f619ede975","tid":1030921,"uid":12599,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"Len Chan 正確答案：A Call B去display。<br />\n其實你哋係咪搏屌&hellip;&hellip;？根本應該係俾個api，跟住return xml/json，之後你哋website都係同公衆一樣咁call個api先啱&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nNelson Chan 你整個app 用api call 野既時候係人讀定機讀？？？？？？<br />\n你搵人 real time 讀完再return 番落個response 度阿？<br />\n<br />\nLouis Sze Chung Li 你哋搵個識IT嘅出post啦。。。"},{"pid":"dd1f486eaf5b2aeb8a774d36714ab33ed659ed90","tid":1030921,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:04:57.000Z","msg":"屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4184c015c26c05c8d87047127f20a90ab2b3a6","tid":1030921,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />CSV, JSON, XML 正呀"},{"pid":"b90de4bd03008a97baee9b1d8af1486a97d6921b","tid":1030921,"uid":42340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"cls公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9bfb77f9bb298db9d49f19801da5e76e59cba9","tid":1030921,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:17:30.000Z","msg":"xml <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4971fb6c9b207b9e49bfd492bdee258349e59259","tid":1030921,"uid":55597,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>創新及科技局 Innovation and Technology Bureau HK<br />\nLike This Page &middot; 19 hrs &middot; <br />\n <br />\n今日有報道指，用機讀格式公布開放數據計劃嘅清單會好啲。同樣嘅資料，A同B兩種形式，你會睇得明邊種？<br />\n<br />\n#機讀格式資料要用電腦程式解讀先易明<br />\n#有需要嘅話用晒兩種形式公布都得<br />\n#公布清單係想畀公眾同業界了解各局同部門開放數據集嘅計劃同時間表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1Fz0fF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1Fz0fF.jpg&h=da5d6def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ITBHK/photos/a.1689124714671352/2214961552087663/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FITBHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.1689124714671352%2F2214961552087663%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=37613675\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ITBHK/photos/a.1689124714671352/2214961552087663/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局 Innovation and Technology Bureau HK 謝謝您們的意見😊。這個post是想展示如果單純以機讀格式去公布開放數據計劃，反而有機會令一般公眾難以理解。但既然有意見認為值得以機讀格式公布清單，資科辦當然會從善如流😉，考慮公眾嘅建議，在網頁版外多加個機讀格式啦。早前有關報道指各政策局和部門的開放數據計劃清單只有網頁版本而沒有機讀格式版本，不方便市民。事實上，開放數據計劃下，所有在「資料一線通」網站開放的數據均會以CSV, JSON, XML等機讀格式發放。<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></blockquote><br />\n邊撚到「所有」？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vJ566b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vJ566b.png&h=cce42ade&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局比個兩pat屎出黎叫開放數據？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFHR2Fq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFHR2Fq.png&h=bc25aa5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\njpeg 又有， gif 又有， pdf 又有，機讀？<br />\n連根本唔係開放格式既 xls, xlsx 都有<br />\n可以冇 csv, json, xml<br />\n<br />\n政府只係將 D result 掉上網就叫開放數據"},{"pid":"dee4dbbfa1fe360eb262991222f16d3dbaa2ea7c","tid":1030921,"uid":28279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你呢啲垃圾使咁多錢，同統計處天文台一撚樣俾啲唔方便既數據"},{"pid":"af1d032c84acdc3be63e18d6d7847098107b8165","tid":1030921,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"不如摺埋個創科局啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa68c6972452542effbec981dbaf294f018c0471","tid":1030921,"uid":30647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:42:05.000Z","msg":"屌, 用紙出 hard copy 算啦。<br />\n網頁都要用 &quot;機&quot; 先開到，hard copy 就咁開眼就睇到啦"},{"pid":"b745dbadd6a26539416d55b98ea9a02e1b94518b","tid":1030921,"uid":3,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"<code>Release_Date_eng</code> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機讀就用 timestamp 或者 iso 8601 之類啦"},{"pid":"a8f31aff76f7def94140ba96b60c629e5e9164fc","tid":1030921,"uid":55597,"like":